Package io.github.JeremyBloom.mosdex2.span

Class MsdxJavaSpan.Factory

java.lang.Object
io.github.JeremyBloom.mosdex2.span.MsdxJavaSpan.Factory
All Implemented Interfaces:
MsdxSpan.Factory
Enclosing class:
MsdxJavaSpan
public static class MsdxJavaSpan.Factory
extends java.lang.Object
implements MsdxSpan.Factory
The Span Factory class provides a number of utility methods that create and manipulate Spans. The wrap method puts a Span facade around a Record stream or collection. The create method copies a Record stream or collection into a Span. The union method flatmaps several Spans into a single Span.
